The '''Commission royale d'Histoire''' is the [[Belgium|Belgian]] Royal Historical Commission. It was founded by [[royal decree]] on 22 July 1834.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kcgeschiedenis.be/en/accueil_en.html|title=Royal historical Commission : Home|website=www.kcgeschiedenis.be}}</ref> The commission publishes a journal, the ''Bulletin''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kcgeschiedenis.be/en/publications/bulletin/bulletin_en.html|title=Royal historical Commission : Bulletin|website=www.kcgeschiedenis.be}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kcgeschiedenis.be/en/publications/bulletin/bulletin_en.pdf|title=Royal Historical Commission - Bulletin|publisher=|date=|accessdate=2018-07-10|deadurl=bot: unknown|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305063506/http://www.kcgeschiedenis.be/en/publications/bulletin/bulletin_en.pdf|archivedate=2016-03-05|df=}}</ref>

[[Victor Coremans]] was appointed to the Commission in 1836.{{citation needed|date=April 2017}}

